  ('dietitian-moex-02000', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-107-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', 'ω-6與ω-3脂肪酸的比較，下列何者正確？', '["ω-3脂肪酸可以代謝成arachidonic acid，藉此促進發炎反應", "ω-6脂肪酸可以代謝成docosahexaenoic acid，藉此促進發炎反應", "ω-6與ω-3脂肪酸的命名，是指從脂肪酸的羧基端（COOH）算起的第一個雙鍵的位置", "一般飲食中，ω-6脂肪酸含量通常高於ω-3脂肪酸"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "81a07d782b21", "answer_pdf_sha1": "811659f781aa", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107030", "c": "103", "s": "0202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "營養學", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 11, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
